# Protected Endpoints

All routes below require:

```
Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN
```

---

## Get Current User

```
GET /v1/u/me
```

Response `200`:

```json
{
  "message": "User successfully fetched",
  "user": {
    "userId": 1,
    "name": "John",
    "surname": "Doe",
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "isActive": true,
    "timezone": "Europe/Istanbul",
    "lastLoginAt": "2026-03-12T12:00:00Z",
    "createdAt": "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z"
  }
}
```

---

## Logout

```
POST /v1/u/auth/logout
```

No request body.

Response `200`:

```json
{
  "message": "Successfully logged out"
}
```

> Clears the `refresh_token` cookie and deactivates the current session.

