# Notifications

## Register Push Token

```
POST /v1/u/notifications/tokens
```

Request:

```json
{
  "token": "FCM_OR_APNs_TOKEN",
  "platform": "ios",
  "deviceId": "optional-device-id",
  "appVersion": "1.0.0"
}
```

Platform options: `ios`, `android`, `web`

Response `201`:

```json
{
  "message": "Device Token successfully created."
}
```

---

## Delete Push Token

```
DELETE /v1/u/notifications/tokens
```

Request:

```json
{
  "token": "FCM_OR_APNs_TOKEN"
}
```

Response `200`:

```json
{
  "message": "Device token successfully deactivated"
}
```

